caption.text: Step by step "How do I edit my previous photo?" ---------------------------------------------  Make a necessary adjustment on original photo.  Load it to Fotolr PS apps, go to "frame" apply the frame which you like. You can apply multiple frame.  To add 3D effect on the photo, I go to Color - ColorFX - Art and apply "Dark Engraving" and the save the photo to your camera roll.  Load the photo to Camera+ apps and apply Filter Red Scale on 60% oppacity. You can play with the preffered filter bases on your photo. -------------------------------------------- i hope it answered your question @agnesnovi @axioma
